WEBVTT

00:04:57.032 --> 00:05:00.215
and are able to enhance the creativity
of the most creative people.

00:05:00.239 --> 00:05:01.684
SD: That's really interesting.

00:05:01.708 --> 00:05:03.896
Would the mechanism
by which they fail or copy

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:07.458
be that they are risk averse?

00:05:07.482 --> 00:05:08.664
AG: I think so, yeah.

00:05:08.688 --> 00:05:09.887
SD: That's interesting.

00:05:09.911 --> 00:05:12.998
I don't know if you've written about this
or where I've read it,

00:05:13.022 --> 00:05:15.531
but I do know that
meeting culture, generally --

00:05:15.555 --> 00:05:18.912
